OL,3,CIndustrial action continues despite
OL,4,CStormont restoration progress
OL,6,FTrade union strikes have again brought
OL,7,Fpublic transport services to a
OL,8,Fstandstill this Thursday.
OL,10,FSchool support workers are also
OL,11,Fengaging in a 48-hour walk-out over
OL,12,Fongoing disputes about pay.
OL,14,FOn January 18, tens of thousands of
OL,15,Fpublic sector workers took part in an
OL,17,FThe latest wave of industrial action
OL,18,Fcomes as which could see the
OL,19,Frestoration of the Northern Ireland's
OL,20,Fdevolved institutions in the coming
OL,21,Fdays.
