OL,3,CIndustrial action continues despite
OL,4,CStormont restoration progress
OL,6,FChris Heaton-Harris has been urged to
OL,7,Frelease funding to make delayed pay
OL,8,Fawards in the absence of a functioning
OL,9,Fdevolved government.
OL,11,FThe Secretary of State has refused,
OL,12,Fsaying the matter is a devolved one.
OL,14,FThe Government has offered a financial
OL,15,Fpackage worth more than #3 billion to
OL,16,Faccompany the return of a devolved
OL,17,FExecutive in Belfast.
OL,19,FA portion of which has been ringfenced
OL,20,Ffor public sector pay awards.
