OL,3,CIndustrial action continues despite
OL,4,CStormont restoration progress
OL,6,FSome members of the public and
OL,7,Fbusiness leaders have called on unions
OL,8,Fto suspend strike action in
OL,9,Frecognition of the progress being made
OL,10,Ftowards a return to powersharing.
OL,12,FPeter Macklin, Regional Organiser of
OL,13,Ftransport union GMB said: "Regardless
OL,14,Fof the latest developments at
OL,15,FStormont, our members are still facing
OL,16,Fthe prospect of a zero percent offer
OL,17,Fmade last year being imposed.
